             Statement of CppADCodeGen Authorship and Copyright
             ==================================================

CppADCodeGen is developed by Joao Rui Leal and Bradley M. Bell and its source 
code is based upon the code of CppAD which was developed by Bradley M. Bell.

The original CppAD library copyright holder is Bradley M. Bell, while the 
